items.title: McConaughey visits local high schoolers
items.summary: High school can be, to put it mildly, rough. There's the mundanity of homework, the stress of figuring out the next step of life and when that's mixed with the pressures of performing well enough to keep grades up, results can slip.

items.title: Cervelli holding out hope for return this season
items.summary: The Pirates only have 15 games remaining after Thursday's off-day in Cincinnati, but catcher Francisco Cervelli still hopes to return from the disabled list before the end of the season.
